Download TIGER shapes for Alaska Native Regional Corporation (Alaska)

Source: R/anrc.R
tt_anrc.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Alaska Native Regional Corporation (Alaska)

Usage

tt_anrc(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_anrc()
